herDuck Obsidian RAG","line":136},{"title":"C-042 RAG","target":"C-042 RAG","line":137},{"title":"图像","target":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HE9lveObMAAN8zu?format=jpg&name=large","line":176,"embedded":true},{"title":"《如何基于 Obsidian 和 Claude 打造 AI 时代超级大脑？》","target":"https://x.com/yanhua1010/status/2020342019575673223?s=20","line":218},{"title":"《Obsidian + Claude Code：你的笔记库就是你最强大的 AI 上下文》","target":"https://x.com/yanhua1010/status/2029369274847072591?s=20","line":219},{"title":"《我用 Podwise 把播客变成了可检索的知识库》","target":"https://x.com/yanhua1010/status/2033726054351966613?s=20","line":220},{"title":"@yanhua1010","target":"https://x.com/@yanhua1010","line":224}],"metadata":{"title":"用 LLM + Obsidian 构建个人知识库：基于 Karpathy 的“LLM Knowledge Bases”工作流","source":"https://x.com/yanhua1010/article/2039966047378583815","author":["[[Yanhua (@yanhua1010)]]"],"published":"2026-04-03","created":"2026-04-04","description":"Karpathy 今天发了一条推文，讲他怎么用 LLM 构建和管理个人知识库。我反复读了几遍。不是因为什么新概念，是因为他做的事和我这几个月在 Obsidian 里瞎折腾的东西，结构上撞了。但他用了一个词来概括，我之前一直没找到：编译（Compile）。把原始资料\"编译\"成结构化...","tags":["#clippings"]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[[46,56],[74,93],[131,154]]},"smart_blocks:8-Raw/Clippings/用 LLM + Obsidian 构建个人知识库：基于 Karpathy 的“LLM Knowledge Bases”工作流.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"1wrfvno","at":1776572951439},"key":"8-Raw/Clippings/用 LLM + Obsidian 构建个人知识库：基于 Karpathy 的“LLM Knowledge Bases”工作流.md#---frontmatter---","lines":[1,11],"size":406,"outlinks":[{"title":"Yanhua (@yanhua1010)","target":"Yanhua (@yanhua1010)","line":5}],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
